data.description:
This beautiful, charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is located in a family friendly neighborhood in the beautiful city of Siloam Springs!
Enjoy an inviting, open living area when you first walk in. It boasts a split floor plan. Spacious and inviting, with a cozy corner gas log fireplace. Galley style kitchen with pantry, features rustic-style cabinets, opens to dining area. Large master is generously sized & other two bedrooms are very well-sized. 

This home is newly renovated and has been thoroughly updated, new flooring, fixtures, rustic barn style fence, new paint inside & out, new A/C unit, among many more!

Make memories with flat open front and back yard with potential for picnic areas for entertaining your family. Spacious side entry two-car garage.

What are you waiting for? Perfect for growing families! Conveniently located less than 2 miles to John Brown University, Downtown, all schools, Sager Creek, City Parks, Biking/Running Trails, Library, Walmart, etc.
A must see! Schedule your showing today!
